Package: hfdatalibrary
Type: Package
Title: Client for the HF Data Library
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ahmed", "Elkassabgi", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "admin@hfdatalibrary.com")
Description: Access free, research-grade 1-minute OHLCV data for U.S. equities
    and ETFs from the HF Data Library (hfdatalibrary.com), in raw and clean
    versions across eight timeframes. Returns tidy data frames.
